        "Name": "Honing Your Hammer",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nThe secret to hammer\u2014 Well,\r\nlet\u0027s not kid ourselves here...\r\nHammer equals thrashing and\r\npummeling your target. Go hunt\r\nthis \u003CCOL RED\u003EPukei-Pukei\u003C/COL\u003E and \u003CCOL RED\u003EBarroth\u003C/COL\u003E and\r\nyou\u0027ll know exactly what I mean!",
